These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta, milk
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, artichoke, grapes
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, fishing, writing
The people have 3 different jobs:  manager, musician, teacher
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, techno, folk
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, chinese, canadian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, surfing, badminton
 1. the person who's sport is volleyball is the chinese##1
 2. the person who's sport is badminton is the teacher##1
 3. the person drinking milk is between the canadian and the person drinking fanta##2
 4. the fan of techno is on the left of the argentine##1
 5. the musician is the person eating grapes##1
 6. the person who's hobby is writing is the argentine##1
 7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
 8. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the fan of soul##1
 9. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the musician##1
10. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | fanta    | milk   | hot-chocolate           |
| Food          | artichoke       | grapes    | lettuce         |
| Hobby         | fishing    | writing  | collecting        |
| Job           | manager | musician   | teacher      |
| Music-Genre   | techno        | folk    | soul       |
| Nationality   | chinese     | argentine  | canadian       |
| Sport         | volleyball     | surfing | badminton |

