.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, milk
There 3 different types of food: tomato, pumpkin, spinach
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, spy, martial-arts
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, folk, country
There are 3 different nationalities: thai, turkish, indonesian
3 different pets are kept: hamster, snake, lizard
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, tennis, lacrosse
 1. the owner of the lizard is the turkish##1
 2. the owner of the lizard is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 4. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking cola##2
 5. the indonesian is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is the fan of r&b##1
 7. the fan of folk is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 8. the person eating tomato is the person watching romance movies##1
 9. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the fan of country##1
10. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | cola   | milk    | soy-milk         |
| Food          | tomato    | pumpkin | spinach          |
| Movie-Genre   | romance  | martial-arts  | spy     |
| Music-Genre   | country       | folk      | r&b         |
| Nationality   | indonesian      | turkish   | thai    |
| Pet           | hamster        | lizard      | snake         |
| Sport         | tennis | parkour  | lacrosse |

