.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: cherry, pepper, grapefruit
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, woodworking, video-games
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, superhero, fantasy
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, jazz, blues
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, polish, german
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, turtle, pony
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, water-polo, skateboarding
 1. the person eating pepper is the owner of the turtle##1
 2. the german is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 3. the person watching animation movies is the person eating grapefruit##1
 4. the person watching superhero movies is the owner of the turtle##1
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 6. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 7. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the polish and the fan of blues##2
 8. the polish is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
 9. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
10. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
11. the polish is the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Food          | grapefruit      | pepper      | cherry      |
| Hobby         | reading   | video-games | woodworking |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | superhero    | fantasy          |
| Music-Genre   | jazz       | reggae      | blues          |
| Nationality   | polish    | brazilian  | german      |
| Pet           | chinchilla   | turtle  | pony        |
| Sport         | golf  | water-polo   | skateboarding     |

