The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, folk, punk
There are 3 different nationalities: american, spanish, australian
3 different pets are kept: bird, frog, pony
 1. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 2. the person drinking water is the australian##1
 3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 4. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 5. the fan of trance is between the person watching animation movies and the person drinking water##2
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 7. the fan of trance is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 8. the dancer is the owner of the pony##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is between the dancer and the pilot##2
10. the australian is on the left of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |       3       |
| Beverage      | water | mirinda           | fanta      |
| Hobby         | baking       | camping         | singing       |
| Job           | dancer    | entrepreneur | pilot |
