3 different pets are kept: cat, hedgehog, goat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, badminton, snowboarding
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, jet-ski, trike
 1. the person eating teamelon is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 2. the person driving the ship is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 3. the person drinking tea is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is badminton and the fan of country##2
 6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is cycling and the owner of the goat##2
 7. the person driving the ship is between the person eating garlic and the person drinking fanta##2
 8. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 9. the entrepreneur is on the right of the fan of techno##1
10. the bartender is the person eating garlic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage      | fanta          | tea         | sprite      |
