11. the person driving the helicopter is the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | sprite      | cola      |
| Hobby         | card-games     | fishing     | sudoku  |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | animation  | martial-arts |
| Nationality   | french  | egyptian     | argentine |
| Pet           | cat        | ferret | goat     |
| Sport         | surfing    | swimming | snowboarding   |
| Transport     | roller        | trike        | helicopter   |

