.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, sprite
There 3 different types of food: kale, grapefruit, peas
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, magic-tricks, traveling
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, librarian, software-developer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, iced-teasy, family
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, golf, badminton
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, bus, snowmobile
1. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the software-developer##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person eating peas##1
3. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the bartender##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person watching romance movies and the librarian##2
5. the person eating peas is between the software-developer and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person eating peas##1
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
8. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
9. the person watching iced-teasy movies is on the left of the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea      | coffee      | sprite       |
| Food          | grapefruit      | peas    | kale   |
| Hobby         | traveling    | writing     | magic-tricks     |
| Job           | librarian    | bartender | software-developer   |
| Movie-Genre   | iced-teasy    | family    | romance       |
| Sport         | badminton | volleyball      | golf    |
| Transport     | bus       | motorbike | snowmobile |

