There 3 different types of food: grapes, nectarine, onion
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, sudoku, skydiving
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, zombie, martial-arts
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, techno, ambient
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, parkour, skateboarding
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, subway, bike
1. the person driving the subway is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
5. the person eating nectarine is between the person drinking water and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
6. the person eating onion is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the fan of techno##1
8. the person driving the boat is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

