.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, almond-milk, coffee
There 3 different types of food: strawberry, pineapple, cucumber
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, electrician, bartender
There are 3 different nationalities: german, american, nigerian
3 different pets are kept: horse, snake, rat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, sailing, soccer
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, taxi, skateboard
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person eating cucumber##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the journalist is between the person drinking coffee and the owner of the rat##2
4. the german is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
7. the electrician is the person eating strawberry##1
8. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
9. the american is between the person eating strawberry and the person driving the boat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk    | hot-chocolate       | coffee      |
| Food          | strawberry   | cucumber   | pineapple  |
| Job           | electrician  | journalist | bartender    |
| Nationality   | german   | american     | nigerian  |
| Pet           | rat     | horse        | snake |
| Sport         | sailing | badminton   | soccer  |
| Transport     | taxi    | skateboard     | boat      |

 